00:01:21.650 --> 00:01:22.800
The Radiesse was just fabulous.

00:01:22.800 --> 00:01:26.990
I mean, it looks absolutely natural, my cheeks
are filled in, it's just, I'm thrilled.

00:01:26.990 --> 00:01:27.990
I'm really thrilled.

00:01:27.990 --> 00:01:33.450
Bridget Kelly: It's nice to be able to have
a tool like this to replace that overall volume

00:01:33.450 --> 00:01:36.850
rather than just always filling a line or
a wrinkle.

