It's a good idea for most patients to come
back at that 3-month mark, where most of the

00:01:42.230 --> 00:01:46.340
gel has been reabsorbed and you've gotten
that collagen stimulation.

00:01:46.340 --> 00:01:51.890
At that point, we can be sure that the patient
has had maximum correction and add another

00:01:51.890 --> 00:01:54.390
